{
  "stem": "15991.3",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it was my job every evening to secure the glass door to the outside to the garden with mattresses and ropes to shield us from possible flying glass.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I remember that job was a tedious job to do.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Then in the morning, take it all down again.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But there we slept for us for many months.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And when the bombing got too bad, we all got up and gathered together in the kitchen and had something to eat, just as a relief, because it was a very nerve-wracking time.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And of course, we all craved sugar and we were very much rationed.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And everybody had their own pot of jam, one pound a month or something like that.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Mine was always gone the first, because I seemed to crave this sugar more than anybody else, so-- so then I had to go to others and ask them for a little bit of jam.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "That was just a little incident.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Luckily, our house was not bombed.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We were living near a lovely piece of land called Hampstead Heath, where the big guns were.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And we kind of-- whenever they went off, we knew they were doing their bit and shooting trying to shoot down the enemy.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And that was quite-- I felt quite protective in spite of the enormous noise they made.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "[SIGHS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This was my adolescence, oh yes, absolutely.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So there was no dating, there were no parties.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, there was a little bit of dating because of my future husband.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And his mother also had got out of her Hamburg, and his father.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And at one point, his mother lived with us, and he came to visit his mother.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And so we-- and we had written to each other and became friends.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
